  "messages": [
    {
      "id": 1351,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:33",
      "content": "The S-Deck UI displays commit messages as one long line — newlines from the commit message are not rendered as line breaks.\n\n**Fix:** In `public/app.js`, find where commit message text is rendered (likely in the task detail panel or commit metadata section). Ensure newlines (`\\n`) in the commit message string are preserved/rendered as `<br>` or the element uses `white-space: pre-wrap` CSS so multiline commit messages display correctly.\n\nApply the same fix wherever commit metadata (subject, body) is displayed inline in the UI.\n\n**Worktree:**\nRun: `synapse worktree create developer-33-fix-commit-linebreaks`\nWork in `.synapse/worktrees/developer-33-fix-commit-linebreaks`. Commit. Do not push.\n\nReport DONE with what you changed.",
      "priority": 5,
      "created_at": 1780914862830,
      "read_at": 1780914865112,
      "needs_approval": 0,
      "approved_at": null,
      "request_options": null,
      "selected_option": null,
      "task_id": null,
      "type": null
    },
    {
      "id": 1353,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:33",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "DONE — Task: Fix commit message line breaks in diff modal\n\n**Root cause:** In `renderDiff()`, all lines (including the commit header, file stats, and unchanged context lines) were wrapped in plain inline `<span>` elements and joined with `''`. Inline spans produce no line breaks, so the entire diff ran together as one long line. The `display:block` CSS on `.diff-add`/`.diff-del`/`.diff-hunk` accidentally masked the bug for colored lines, but plain context lines had no block layout.\n\n**Fix (public/app.js):**\n- Context/unchanged lines now emit as raw text nodes with a trailing `\\n` instead of an inline `<span>`. The `<pre>` parent with `white-space:pre` preserves them correctly.\n- `+++`/`---` file-header lines now use a new `diff-hdr` class (display:block) instead of falling through to the inline path.\n\n**Fix (public/style.css):**\n- Added `.diff-hdr { display:block; color:var(--muted) }` rule.\n\n**Files changed:**\n- `public/app.js`: renderDiff context-line and header-line handling\n- `public/style.css`: new .diff-hdr rule\n\n**Build:** clean. **Commit:** `0912af1` on `synapse/developer-33-fix-commit-linebreaks`.",
      "priority": 5,
      "created_at": 1780915058578,
      "read_at": 1780915060853,
      "needs_approval": 0,
      "approved_at": null,
      "request_options": null,
      "selected_option": null,
      "task_id": null,
      "type": "done"
    }
  ],
